Package org.ginsim.core.graph.regulatorygraph

Class RegulatoryNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ginsim.core.graph.regulatorygraph.RegulatoryNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.colomoto.biolqm.NodeInfoHolder, ToolTipsable
    public class RegulatoryNode
extends Object
implements ToolTipsable, org.colomoto.biolqm.NodeInfoHolder
    A node in the Regulatory graph, representing a regulatory component. A component has:
    • a maxValue
    • an annotation (comment and URLs)
    • a dynamical behaviour defined by logical parameters or functions.
    Author:
    Aurelien Naldi.
